author: rwesten
msg: First version of an Indexed in-memory Clerezza TripleCollection/Graph/MGraph implementation (will create Clerezza issue soon™)
See JavaDoc of the IndexedTripleCollection for Details.

This currently passes the UnitTests also used for SimpleTripleCollection. In addition there is an additional test that validates the implementation of the filter(..) method based on the results of the SimpleTripleCollection implementation.
Currently there are no special tests for other features. Especially GraphEvent support and detailed tests for add/remove ... would be great!
